description: It contains the main body of the “Development Data Book”(pages 01 to 61) as of December 17, 2012. The Development Data Book lists all of the Authority's Developments alphabetically and includes information on the development identification numbers, program and construction type, number of apartments and rental rooms, population, number of buildings and stories, street boundaries, and political districts.
